WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:27.340 --> 00:00:30.460
I'm leaving now. I'll let you know when the press arrive and bring them here, ok?

00:00:31.740 --> 00:00:33.580
Great, thank you Sandra

00:00:41.720 --> 00:00:51.520
[investor speaks in foreign language]

00:00:55.980 --> 00:00:57.940
What happened here?

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:03.380
[VCF rep] Did you hear anything of what he said?

00:01:03.620 --> 00:01:06.180
[José] I only understood Alcacer, Feghouli, Negredo…

00:01:06.380 --> 00:01:08.540
[VCF rep to Investor] Ok, alright. He needs to make a decision by himself.

00:01:08.740 --> 00:01:12.940
[VCF rep] Ok, so apparently he wants to invite a friend to the event at the Megastore.

00:01:13.300 --> 00:01:17.520
But there are no tickets, so he wants your pass. He'll pay...

00:01:19.520 --> 00:01:20.500
[Investor] Forty Euros?

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:21.660
Don't feel any pressure to say yes because of us…

00:01:21.860 --> 00:01:23.400
[Ivan] It's not about the money, I just don't think this is the way to ask for something.

00:01:24.960 --> 00:01:26.255
[José] I would do anything for Valencia CF

00:01:26.540 --> 00:01:28.340
[Investor] Four thousand Euros?

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:34.200
[VCF rep] It's all up to you

00:01:36.800 --> 00:01:38.660
[José] No, no, no. I don't want anything

00:01:39.160 --> 00:01:40.300
[Iván] No, no no

00:01:40.580 --> 00:01:41.720
[Toni] No. Make it clear: no.

00:01:41.860 --> 00:01:43.000
[Iván] No, it's a unique opportunity

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:44.340
[Toni] No. I carry Valencia in my heart.

00:01:46.260 --> 00:01:49.440
And now say hello, because this is a hidden camera prank!

00:01:56.280 --> 00:01:57.660
[Toni] I wouldn't miss it for anything.

00:02:07.320 --> 00:02:09.060
[Iván] Let's go, let's get on the bus!

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:19.400
[Iván] Now we're first off the bus...

00:02:21.960 --> 00:02:24.380
[José] Let's have some applause, we're the new signings!

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:31.260
[Toni] We'll be the first ones to put our feet in the Megastore!

00:02:31.480 --> 00:02:33.040
[José] This is the dream of every Valencia CF fan.

00:02:33.100 --> 00:02:34.620
[Iván] I think we're heading inside...

00:02:37.820 --> 00:02:38.700
[José] He is a really friendly guy...

00:02:45.380 --> 00:02:46.440
[Iván] This is amazing!

